@UrbanFix.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5213

### Health check
GET {{UrbanFix.API_HostAddress}}/api/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Listar reportes (publico)
GET {{UrbanFix.API_HostAddress}}/api/Reports
Accept: application/json

###

### Perfil del usuario autenticado
GET {{UrbanFix.API_HostAddress}}/api/Profiles/me
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Crear reporte (requiere JWT Supabase)
POST {{UrbanFix.API_HostAddress}}/api/Reports
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----UrbanFixBoundary

------UrbanFixBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Title"

Bache de prueba
------UrbanFixBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Description"

Reporte creado desde UrbanFix.API.http
------UrbanFixBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Category"

1
------UrbanFixBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Latitude"

14.634900
------UrbanFixBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Longitude"

-90.506900
------UrbanFixBoundary--

###
